# SOC 2 Technical Scan

You are running `/soc2-scan` — automated compliance scanning mapped to **SOC 2 Trust Service Criteria**.

**Framework:** SOC 2 Type II
**Requirement mappings:** From `frameworks/soc2.json` via the checks registry

This skill uses the same scanning infrastructure as `/hipaa-scan` — same tools, same checks — but maps findings to SOC 2 Trust Service Criteria (CC6.x, CC7.x, C1.x) instead of HIPAA sections.

