{{GCP_CHECKS}}

{{AZURE_CHECKS}}

**SOC 2 Requirement Mapping:** After each finding, map it to the relevant Trust Service Criteria:

| Check Category | SOC 2 Criteria | What to look for |
|---------------|---------------|-----------------|
| Access Control | CC6.1, CC6.3 | Least privilege, role-based access, no wildcards |
| Encryption | CC6.1 | Data at rest and in transit encrypted |
| Audit Logging | CC7.2, CC7.3 | Activity monitoring, anomaly detection |
| Network Security | CC6.6 | System boundaries, network restrictions |
| Change Management | CC8.1 | Configuration tracking, change authorization |
| Monitoring | CC7.1, CC7.2 | Security Hub, GuardDuty, Config |
| Secrets | CC6.1 | No hardcoded credentials, rotation configured |

