## Phase 3: Code-Level Scan

{{PHI_PATTERNS}}

**Note:** For SOC 2, these patterns detect sensitive data exposure broadly — not just health data. Look for PII (names, emails, SSNs), financial data, authentication credentials, and any data classified as confidential in the system description.

