## Phase 6: Dashboard Updates

Update the dashboard with SOC 2 findings. Use `--framework soc2` to ensure findings are tracked under the SOC 2 framework:

```bash
_EMDASH_BIN=$([ -d ~/.claude/skills/em-dash/bin ] && echo ~/.claude/skills/em-dash/bin || echo .claude/skills/em-dash/bin)
"$_EMDASH_BIN"/hipaa-dashboard-update --framework soc2 finding add --title "<title>" --severity <severity> --requirement "<CC6.x>" --source "soc2-scan"
```

For checklist updates:
```bash
"$_EMDASH_BIN"/hipaa-dashboard-update --framework soc2 checklist "<CC6.1>" complete "<reasoning>"
```

